}整理一下以上内容的格式，我要写入~/.claude/settings.json

```json
{
  "hooks": {
    "Stop": [
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "~/.claude/hooks/notify_feishu.py --event stop",
            "timeout": 10
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "Notification": [
      {
        "matcher": "idle_prompt",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "~/.claude/hooks/notify_feishu.py --event idle",
            "timeout": 10
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "permission_prompt",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "~/.claude/hooks/notify_feishu.py --event permission",
            "timeout": 10
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

这个格式已经整理好了，可以直接写入 `~/.claude/settings.json` 文件。配置包含了三个钩子：
- **Stop**: 当停止时触发飞书通知
- **idle_prompt**: 当进入空闲状态时触发通知
- **permission_prompt**: 当需要权限确认时触发通知
